  <entry>
    <title>时间标准</title>
    <url>/2018/01/23/Date/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="UTC：协调世界时"><a href="#UTC：协调世界时" class="headerlink" title="UTC：协调世界时"></a>UTC：协调世界时</h2><blockquote>
<p>协调世界时（英：Coordinated Universal Time ，法：Temps Universel Coordonné），又称世界统一时间，世界标准时间，国际协调时间。英文（CUT）和法文（TUC）的缩写不同，作为妥协，简称UTC。<br>世界标准时间UTC：GMT+0</p>
</blockquote>
<p>2016-08-9T10:01:54.123Z</p>
<p>T代表后面跟着的是时间</p>
<p>Z代表0时区UTC统一时间（慢北京时间8小时）</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<hr>
<h2 id="GMT：格林尼治平时"><a href="#GMT：格林尼治平时" class="headerlink" title="GMT：格林尼治平时"></a>GMT：格林尼治平时</h2><blockquote>
<p>世界时UT 即格林尼治时间，格林尼治所在地的标准时间。以地球自转为基础的时间计量系统。地球自转的角度可用地方子午线相对于地球上的基本参考点的运动来度量。为了测量地球自转，人们在地球上选取了两个基本参考点：春分点（见分至点）和平太阳，由此确定的时间分别称为恒星时和平太阳时。<br>但是格林尼治本地的时间比格林尼治平时，大一小时，也就是格林尼治本地的时间：GMT+1</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Thu Oct 16 07:13:48 GMT 2015</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="CST：也就是北京时间"><a href="#CST：也就是北京时间" class="headerlink" title="CST：也就是北京时间"></a>CST：也就是北京时间</h2><blockquote>
<p>澳洲中部时间，Central Standard Time (Australia)中部标准时区（北美洲），Central Standard Time (North America)北京时间，China Standard Time古巴标准时间，Cuba Standard Time，参见北美东部时区</p>
<p>通常我们在数据库中存放，或者给用户看的时间都是CST时间<br>北京时间CST：UTC+8</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Thu Sep 08 23:14:00 CST 2011</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="ISO-8601-：表现日期和时间的国际标准"><a href="#ISO-8601-：表现日期和时间的国际标准" class="headerlink" title="ISO 8601 ：表现日期和时间的国际标准"></a>ISO 8601 ：表现日期和时间的国际标准</h2><blockquote>
<p><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%8C%96%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87/779832">国际标准化组织</a>的国际标准ISO 8601是日期和时间的表示方法，全称为《数据存储和交换形式·信息交换·日期和时间的表示方法》。最新为第三版ISO8601:2004，第一版为ISO8601:1988，第二版为ISO8601:2000。</p>
</blockquote>
<p>2017-09-30T09:00:00</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="UNIX时间戳"><a href="#UNIX时间戳" class="headerlink" title="UNIX时间戳"></a>UNIX时间戳</h2><blockquote>
<p>计算机中的UNIX时间戳，是以GMT/UTC时间「1970-01-01T00:00:00」为起点，到具体时间的秒数，不考虑闰秒。这么做当然是为了简化计算机对时间操作的复杂度。</p>
</blockquote>
<p>1633786697</p>
<blockquote>
<p><em>！如有错误请在评论及时指出</em></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>知识点</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>基石</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>JavaScript 常用代码段</title>
    <url>/2019/10/07/JavaScript-Skills/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>JavaScript 编写中可能用到的技巧，熟练运用后说不定会有事半功倍的效果</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="Quick-Console-log"><a href="#Quick-Console-log" class="headerlink" title="Quick Console.log"></a>Quick Console.log</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> c = <span class="built_in">console</span>.log.bind(<span class="built_in">document</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> info = <span class="built_in">console</span>.info.bind(<span class="built_in">document</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    c(<span class="string">&quot;This is JavaScript&quot;</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    c(<span class="literal">true</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    c(<span class="number">12345</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    info(<span class="string">&quot;This is JavaScript&quot;</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    info(<span class="literal">true</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    info(<span class="number">12345</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>更加简短的 console.log() 或者是 console.info() </p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="箭头函数"><a href="#箭头函数" class="headerlink" title="箭头函数"></a>箭头函数</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">print1</span>(<span class="params"></span>) </span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> print2 = <span class="function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">sum</span>(<span class="params">x, y</span>) </span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="keyword">return</span> x + y</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> sum2 = <span class="function">(<span class="params">x, y</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="keyword">return</span> x + y</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>通过箭头函数有效减少代码量，熟悉后更易阅读</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Spread-Operator"><a href="#Spread-Operator" class="headerlink" title="Spread Operator"></a>Spread Operator</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="comment">// Array connection</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> num1 = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> num2 = [<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> concat = [...num1, ...num2]                 <span class="comment">// [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(concat)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="comment">// Copying An Array</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> alpha = [<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;b&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;c&#x27;</span>]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> copy = [...alpha]                           <span class="comment">// [&#x27;a&#x27;,&#x27;b&#x27;,&#x27;c&#x27;]</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(copy)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="comment">// Array literals</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> data = [<span class="number">100</span>, <span class="number">200</span>]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> literal = [...data, <span class="number">300</span>, <span class="number">400</span>, <span class="number">500</span>]          <span class="comment">// [100,200,300,400,500]</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(literal)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>展开运算符(ES6)，它接受一个可迭代对象并将其扩展为单个元素</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Truncating-an-array"><a href="#Truncating-an-array" class="headerlink" title="Truncating an array"></a>Truncating an array</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> arr = [<span class="number">100</span>, <span class="number">200</span>, <span class="number">300</span>, <span class="number">400</span>, <span class="number">500</span>, <span class="number">600</span>]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    arr.length = <span class="number">3</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(arr)                                <span class="comment">// [100,200,300]</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    arr.length = <span class="number">0</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(arr)                                <span class="comment">// []</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>length 方法不仅可以显示字符串大小，还可以将数组截断为任意大小</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Smart-Replacing"><a href="#Smart-Replacing" class="headerlink" title="Smart Replacing"></a>Smart Replacing</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> str = <span class="string">&quot;This is potato and potato&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(str.replace(<span class="regexp">/pot/</span>, <span class="string">&quot;tom&quot;</span>))          <span class="comment">// This is tomato and potato</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(str.replace(<span class="regexp">/pot/g</span>, <span class="string">&quot;tom&quot;</span>))         <span class="comment">// This is tomato and tomato</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>替换特定词</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Numerical-Separator"><a href="#Numerical-Separator" class="headerlink" title="Numerical Separator"></a>Numerical Separator</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> data1 = <span class="number">10_0000</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> data2 = <span class="number">3_0000_0000</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(data1)                              <span class="comment">// 100000</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(data2)                              <span class="comment">// 300000000</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>这个简单的技巧可以提高 JavaScript 大量数据的可读性</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Quick-Power-Calculation"><a href="#Quick-Power-Calculation" class="headerlink" title="Quick Power Calculation"></a>Quick Power Calculation</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="comment">// Normal Way</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="built_in">Math</span>.pow(<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>))                     <span class="comment">// 1024</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="built_in">Math</span>.pow(<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">5</span>))                     <span class="comment">// 32</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="comment">// Quick Way</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="number">4</span> ** <span class="number">5</span>)                             <span class="comment">// 1024</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="number">2</span> ** <span class="number">5</span>)                             <span class="comment">// 32</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>pow() 方法来计算任何数字的幂，这个技巧将常规数学方法以快速形式计算次方</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Rest-Parameter"><a href="#Rest-Parameter" class="headerlink" title="Rest Parameter"></a>Rest Parameter</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">sum</span>(<span class="params">...num</span>) </span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="keyword">let</span> cal = <span class="number">0</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">const</span> a <span class="keyword">of</span> num) &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">            cal += a</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(cal)                            <span class="comment">// 27</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    sum(<span class="number">20</span>,<span class="number">7</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>Rest Parameter 语法用于处理函数中定义中的无限数量的参数</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><em>！如有错误请在评论及时指出</em></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>JavaScript</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>技巧</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>JavaScript 格式转换</title>
    <url>/2019/10/11/Javascript-Format/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>JavaScript 中常用的格式转换</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="时间类型"><a href="#时间类型" class="headerlink" title="时间类型"></a>时间类型</h2><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="title">formatTime</span>(<span class="params">time</span>)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">let</span> date = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Date</span>(time).toJSON()</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Date</span>(+<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Date</span>(date) + <span class="number">8</span> * <span class="number">3600</span> * <span class="number">1000</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        .toISOString()</span><br><span class="line">        .replace(<span class="regexp">/T/g</span>, <span class="string">&#x27; &#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        .replace(<span class="regexp">/\.[\d]&#123;3&#125;Z/</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>传入的参数时间格式为 <a href="https://sndshun.xyz/Standardization/Date/">UTC格式</a>                   2019-10-09T13:51:25.414Z</p>
<p>将参数时间转换暂存                                       2019-10-09T13:51:25.414Z</p>
<p>返回一个新的时间=参数时间+8*3600（60分钟 x 60秒）x1000毫秒 [八小时] 变为北京时间         2019-10-09T21:51:25.414Z</p>
<p>使用ISO标准将 Date 对象转换为字符串。    2019-10-09T21:51:25.414Z</p>
<p>将T替换为空格                                                 2019-10-09 21:51:25.414Z</p>
<p>将.和Z中间的3个数字包括.和Z替换为空气    2019-10-09 21:51:25</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><em>！如有错误请在评论及时指出</em></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>JavaScript</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>格式转换</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>HTML 实用标签</title>
    <url>/2020/10/30/HTML-tags/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><code>HTML</code>标签是很基础的知识，但偶然间发现一些复杂的第三方组件，用原生标签也可以简单实现。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="颜色选择组件（Color-Picker）"><a href="#颜色选择组件（Color-Picker）" class="headerlink" title="颜色选择组件（Color Picker）"></a>颜色选择组件（Color Picker）</h2><p>在项目中，你可能希望通过调色板组件动态调整颜色，这时你可以使用 <code>&lt;input type=&quot;color&quot;&gt;</code> 就可以轻松调用一个调色板组件，省去你在找第三方组件，示例效果如下：</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sndshun/hosting/img/HTML-tags-color.gif" alt="HTML-tags-color"></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;color&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="引用标签（Blockquote）"><a href="#引用标签（Blockquote）" class="headerlink" title="引用标签（Blockquote）"></a>引用标签（Blockquote）</h2><p>在文章排版时，有时候我们需要引用一些信息，这时我们需要用特殊的样式进行强调，这时你可以使用<code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code> 标签来强调你用的内容，示例效果如下所示</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sndshun/hosting/img/HTML-tags-blockquote.webp" alt="HTML-tags-blockquote"></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;border-left: 3px solid blue&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        For 50 years, WWF has been protecting the future of nature. The worlds leading conservation organization, WWF works in 100 countries and is supported by 1.2 million members in the United States and close to 5 million globally.</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="折叠组件（Accordion）"><a href="#折叠组件（Accordion）" class="headerlink" title="折叠组件（Accordion）"></a>折叠组件（Accordion）</h2><p>折叠列表的需求也是比较常见的，点击标题展开对应的信息内容，这时 <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> 标签就派上用场了，示例效果如下所示：</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sndshun/hosting/img/HTML-tags-accordion.gif" alt="HTML-tags-accordion"></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span>标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>内容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="内容编辑（Content-Editor）"><a href="#内容编辑（Content-Editor）" class="headerlink" title="内容编辑（Content Editor）"></a>内容编辑（Content Editor）</h2><p>为了让内容具有编辑性，你可以不必使用表单组件，比如 input、textarea 标签，你可以在可编辑的容器(div) 上添加 <code>contenteditable</code> 属性，就能很轻松的完成当前容器及所见即所得的编辑，示例如下所示：</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sndshun/hosting/img/HTML-tags-edit.gif" alt="HTML-tags-edit"></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">contenteditable</span>=<span class="string">&quot;true&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	可编辑</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="图片标签（Picture-Tag）"><a href="#图片标签（Picture-Tag）" class="headerlink" title="图片标签（Picture Tag）"></a>图片标签（Picture Tag）</h2><p>有时候需要在不同的分辨率下显示不同的图片，如果你使用<code>&lt;img&gt;</code> 标签的话，你需要做的工作就会许多，但是使用<code>&lt;picture&gt;</code> 标签就能很轻松的完成在不同分辨率下显示不同图片的设置，调整浏览器的大小，就会根据窗口的大小显示不同大小的图片，示例效果如下所示：</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sndshun/hosting/img/HTML-tags-img.jpg" alt="HTML-tags-img"></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">picture</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">source</span> <span class="attr">media</span>=<span class="string">&quot;(min-width: 650px)&quot;</span> <span class="attr">srcset</span>=<span class="string">&quot;url&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">source</span> <span class="attr">media</span>=<span class="string">&quot;(min-width: 465px)&quot;</span> <span class="attr">srcset</span>=<span class="string">&quot;url&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">&lt;!--根据屏幕匹配的不同尺寸显示不同图片，如果没有匹配到或浏览器不支持 picture 属性则使用 img 元素--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;url&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">picture</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="进度条（Progress-Bar）"><a href="#进度条（Progress-Bar）" class="headerlink" title="进度条（Progress Bar）"></a><strong>进度条（Progress Bar）</strong></h2><p>进度条组件也是个很常见的组件，你可以使用<code>&lt;progress&gt;</code> 标签就能轻松完成相关外观的设置，示例效果如下：</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sndshun/hosting/img/HTML-tags-progress.jpg" alt="HTML-tags-progress"></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">progress</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;22&quot;</span> <span class="attr">max</span>=<span class="string">&quot;100&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">progress</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="下拉组件（Dropdown）"><a href="#下拉组件（Dropdown）" class="headerlink" title="下拉组件（Dropdown）"></a>下拉组件（Dropdown）</h2><p>如果下拉组件选项比较多，用户选择就会比较困难，用户可能希望结合输入，能很方便的定位到下拉组件的内容，这时候你可以使用 <code>&lt;datalist&gt;</code> 标签就能满足上述需求，示例效果如下所示：</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sndshun/hosting/img/HTML-tags-dropdown.gif" alt="HTML-tags-dropdown"></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">list</span>=<span class="string">&quot;browsers&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;browser&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">datalist</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;browsers&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;Internet Explorer&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;Firefox&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;Chrome&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;Opera&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;Safari&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">datalist</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="提示框（Tooltip）"><a href="#提示框（Tooltip）" class="headerlink" title="提示框（Tooltip）"></a>提示框（Tooltip）</h2><p>如果你需要对页面某部分进行详细介绍时，你可能需要鼠标经过此区域显示详细的提示框效果，这时我们可以使用 <code>title</code> 属性就能轻松实现，示例效果如下所示：</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sndshun/hosting/img/HTML-tags-tooltip.jpg" alt="HTML-tags-tooltip"></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">title</span>=<span class="string">&quot;这是提示&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    这是内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





<blockquote>
<p><em>！如有错误请在评论及时指出</em></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>HTML</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>HTML</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>Vue3 新特性</title>
    <url>/2021/10/28/Vue3/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>Vue3在2原来的写法上添加了不少新特性，但是也有许多非兼容的变更。稍不留意还是会踩许多坑的，这篇文章就来总结下Vue3的变化</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="组合式API-composition-API"><a href="#组合式API-composition-API" class="headerlink" title="组合式API(composition-API)"></a>组合式API(composition-API)</h2><p><code>setup()</code>函数是Vue3.0中，专门为组件提供的新属性。它为基于<code>Composition API</code>的新特性提供了统一的入口。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>在Vue3中，定义<code>methods</code>、<code>watch</code>、<code>computed</code>、<code>data</code>数据都放在了<code>setup()</code>函数中</p>
<p>根据官网解释，<code>setup()</code>会在<code>data</code>、<code>computed</code>、<code>methods</code>解析前就被调用，所以无法在<code>setup()</code>使用<code>this</code></p>
<p>但是<code>setup()</code>提供参数<code>context</code>来访问<code>Vue</code>的实例this</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="执行时期"><a href="#执行时期" class="headerlink" title="执行时期"></a>执行时期</h3>]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>JavaScript</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Vue</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
